cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SD

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language feedback and learning semantic parsers. It could also belong to "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) and "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as it proposes a learning algorithm for training semantic parsers. Additionally, it could be categorized under "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as the algorithm may involve neural networks, and "cs.SD" (Software Engineering) as it deals with constructing a dataset and developing a learning algorithm.
